Zebulun will live2957  The verb שָׁכַן (shakhan) means “to settle,” but not necessarily as a permanent dwelling place. The tribal settlements by the sea would have been temporary and not the tribe’s territory. by the haven of the sea
and become a haven for ships;
his border will extend to Sidon.2958  For location see Map1-A1; JP3-F3; JP4-F3.

Benjamin is a ravenous wolf;
in the morning devouring the prey,
and in the evening dividing the plunder.”
